<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Oversight and Government Reform:</header><text>Mr. Tom Davis of Virginia.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Rules:</header><text>Mr. Dreier, Mr. Lincoln Diaz-Balart of Florida, Mr. Hastings of Washington, and Mr. Sessions.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

